briefdescription.para: Removes the element at the given index using swap-and-pop.

detaileddescription.para: Uses the swap-and-pop technique for O(1) removal: 1. Move the last element to the position of the removed element 2. Update the sparse array entry for the moved element 3. Pop the last element from dense storage 4. Mark the removed slot as Tombstone
